<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">

{#        fait en sorte que la page soit responsive#}
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

        <title>{% block title %}Welcome!{% endblock %}</title>

{#        favicon (tab icon)#}
        <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="{{asset('assets/img/favicon.png')}}">
        {# Run `composer require symfony/webpack-encore-bundle`
           and uncomment the following Encore helpers to start using Symfony UX #}
        {% block stylesheets %}
            {#{{ encore_entry_link_tags('app') }}#}
        {% endblock %}

        {% block javascripts %}
            {#{{ encore_entry_script_tags('app') }}#}
        {% endblock %}

        {#        font#}
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

        {#        font Logo#}
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oleo+Script+Swash+Caps&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">


        {#        import de bootstrap et d'une feuille de style (style.vss)#}
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <link href="{{ asset('assets/css/style.css') }}" rel="stylesheet"/>

    </head>

    <body>
        <header class="header">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-6 d-flex align-items-center ps-3">
                        <img src="{{asset('assets/img/logo.png')}}" alt="logo">
                        <h3 class="mb-0 mx-1">Bucket List</h3>
                    </div>

{#                    TODO Faire la nav#}
                    <nav class="col-6 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-end pe-5">
                        <div class="">
                            <a class="btnAccueil mx-2" href="{{ path( "app_home" ) }}" style="text-decoration: none;">Accueil</a>
                            <a class="btnAbout mx-2" href="{{ path( "app_about_us" ) }}" style="text-decoration: none;">About Us</a>
                            <a class="btnAjouter mx-2" href="{{ path( "app_idee_form" ) }}" style="text-decoration: none;">Ajouter</a>
                        </div>
                    </nav>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <main class="m-2">

            {% for label, messages in app.flashes %}
                {% for message in messages %}
                    <div class="alert-{{ label }}">
                        {{ message }}
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}
            {% endfor %}

            {% block body %}{% endblock %}
        </main>

        <footer class="bg-secondary">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <div class="row p-2">
                    <div class="div pt-3 text-center">
                        &#169Bucket-List - {{ 'now' | date('Y') }}
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row pt-2 pb-5">
                    <div class="col-4 p-3">
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Animi, asperiores atque blanditiis commodi dicta eius excepturi facilis in iste laborum odit quam quisquam repellendus tempora ut. A dolorum ex voluptates!
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-4 p-3">
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Ad aliquam aliquid aspernatur commodi corporis doloribus ea eaque earum facere facilis hic ipsa ipsam labore libero minus officiis pariatur possimus, sed!
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-4 p-3">
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. A, amet aspernatur autem expedita, iusto laudantium libero, minima molestias quae quas quis vel. Cumque et exercitationem magni, minus officia possimus provident?
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </body>
</html>
